# DineFlow вЂ“ Restaurant Management Web Application

## рџ“Њ Project Overview

DineFlow is a full-stack restaurant portfolio and contact management web application built using **Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB, and EJS**.
The application allows users to explore a restaurant website and submit messages through a contact form.
All messages are stored in **MongoDB**, and the admin can **view, edit, and delete** messages from the admin interface.

This project demonstrates **backend development, database integration, and CRUD operations**.

---

# рџљЂ Features

### Customer Side

* Restaurant portfolio website
* Food menu display
* Customer testimonials
* Contact form for sending messages

### Admin Side

* View all customer messages
* Edit customer messages
* Delete customer messages
* Dynamic data rendering using EJS

---

