# вљ™пёЏ Installation

Clone the repository:

```
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/dineflow.git
```

Go to the project folder:

```
cd dineflow
```

Install dependencies:

```
npm install
```

Start the server:

```
npm start
```

Open in browser:

```
http://localhost:3000
```

---

# рџ§© CRUD Operations

The project implements full **CRUD functionality** for managing customer messages.

| Operation | Description                                   |
| --------- | --------------------------------------------- |
| Create    | Customer submits message through contact form |
| Read      | Admin can view all messages                   |
| Update    | Admin can edit message details                |
| Delete    | Admin can remove messages                     |

---

# рџ—„ Database Schema

